Mr. Fang looks like

00:02:22.439 --> 00:02:24.599
An expert in this field

00:02:24.599 --> 00:02:25.879
Don't be modest

00:02:26.919 --> 00:02:27.520
Niannian

00:02:28.039 --> 00:02:30.120
Do you know what kind of woman is scariest?

00:02:31.680 --> 00:02:32.479
Tell me

00:02:32.479 --> 00:02:33.439
It's the kind

00:02:33.439 --> 00:02:36.360
Who thinks she is very smart

00:02:36.560 --> 00:02:37.520
