00:02:38.879 --> 00:02:40.039
I don't deny it

00:02:40.039 --> 00:02:40.960
That's just how I am

00:02:40.960 --> 00:02:41.879
I am smart

00:02:41.879 --> 00:02:43.639
I think I'm super smart

00:02:44.800 --> 00:02:45.719
Handsome

00:02:46.680 --> 00:02:47.680
