00:02:54.479 --> 00:02:56.879
Hey, don't mind her.

00:02:57.240 --> 00:02:58.719
She just likes to joke around.

00:03:01.080 --> 00:03:01.759
But Niannian,

00:03:01.759 --> 00:03:03.840
