00:03:11.759 --> 00:03:13.719
It doesn't matter if it's a man or woman, right?

00:03:13.719 --> 00:03:14.360
Right?

00:03:14.360 --> 00:03:15.280
Even if it were a woman,

00:03:15.280 --> 00:03:16.879
I'd never date someone close to home.

00:03:18.960 --> 00:03:21.639
So is it a man or someone close to home?

00:03:21.759 --> 00:03:22.479
A man.

00:03:25.639 --> 00:03:26.120
By the way,

00:03:26.520 --> 00:03:27.639
what do you do?

00:03:30.319 --> 00:03:31.879
What kind of work do you do?

00:03:32.960 --> 00:03:34.639
We work on software...

00:03:35.120 --> 00:03:36.560
...social app development.

00:03:36.719 --> 00:03:38.680
Our app is called Peipei.

00:03:38.680 --> 00:03:40.599
It's a free one...

00:03:40.599 --> 00:03:42.520
I actually use Peipei.

00:03:42.520 --> 00:03:43.159
Really?

00:03:43.400 --> 00:03:44.520
You guys developed it?

00:03:45.000 --> 00:03:47.639
To be exact, I developed it.

00:03:48.479 --> 00:03:49.680
That's impressive.

00:03:49.680 --> 00:03:50.280
No, not really.

00:03:51.240 --> 00:03:53.520
It's my first time meeting a software guru.

00:03:53.840 --> 00:03:55.680
Come on, we must add each other as friends.

00:03:59.439 --> 00:04:01.400
Your nickname is just the letter N.

00:04:01.400 --> 00:04:02.520
Does it have any meaning?

00:04:04.199 --> 00:04:05.479
This N...

00:04:05.800 --> 00:04:07.080
like X,

00:04:07.240 --> 00:04:09.639
it represents an unknown variable.

00:04:09.840 --> 00:04:11.280
It makes it seem mysterious.

00:04:11.840 --> 00:04:12.680
How mysterious?

00:04:12.879 --> 00:04:13.639
Well...

00:04:14.120 --> 00:04:15.520
that might require...

00:04:15.520 --> 00:04:17.319
...you to explore it yourself.

00:04:17.319 --> 00:04:19.079
But it might take a long time.

00:04:21.040 --> 00:04:22.040
You're quite slick.

00:04:22.040 --> 00:04:22.959
No, no.

00:04:22.959 --> 00:04:24.040
Come on, let's drink, let's drink.

00:04:24.560 --> 00:04:27.800
You deceived her! You toyed with her feelings!

00:04:27.800 --> 00:04:28.279
I didn't.

00:04:28.279 --> 00:04:30.120
And in the end, you killed her, didn't you?

00:04:30.120 --> 00:04:31.560
No, Auntie, I didn't.

00:04:31.560 --> 00:04:32.120
Auntie Ma.

