Let him finish speaking.

00:04:33.199 --> 00:04:35.040
Yes, yes, Auntie, let me finish.

00:04:35.040 --> 00:04:36.160
I haven't finished yet, Auntie.

00:04:36.360 --> 00:04:37.439
Don't hold anything back.

00:04:37.439 --> 00:04:38.920
Drink more if you can.

00:04:40.319 --> 00:04:41.120
Have fun.

00:04:44.920 --> 00:04:45.959
I'm going to the restroom.

00:04:59.160 --> 00:05:00.439
Let me ask you a question.

00:05:01.120 --> 00:05:01.759
What question?

00:05:02.800 --> 00:05:04.199
Between me and Niannian...

00:05:05.199 --> 00:05:06.439
...who do you like more?

00:05:10.319 --> 00:05:11.319
Huh? What?

00:05:11.319 --> 00:05:13.040
I'm asking you, me or Niannian, who do you choose?

00:05:15.319 --> 00:05:16.680
You're both so outstanding.

00:05:17.040 --> 00:05:18.160
How am I qualified to choose?

00:05:20.360 --> 00:05:21.399
I really hate...

00:05:21.399 --> 00:05:23.079
...ambiguous answers like yours.

00:05:23.439 --> 00:05:25.439
I mean, if the two of us...

00:05:25.439 --> 00:05:27.079
...and you really had to pick one...

00:05:27.439 --> 00:05:28.279
...who would you pick?

00:05:31.439 --> 00:05:32.720
Come on, say it.

00:05:32.720 --> 00:05:33.519
When Niannian comes out in a bit...

00:05:33.519 --> 00:05:34.560
...it'll be so awkward if she hears.

00:05:36.759 --> 00:05:37.360
Well, if I say it...

00:05:37.360 --> 00:05:38.240
...don't get mad.

00:05:40.079 --> 00:05:41.879
Forget it, don't say it. It's awkward.

